2022 succession politics and gender rule debate took centre stage during the burial of Deputy President William Ruto’s personal aide Farouk Kibet’s  father in Chepsaita Turbo constituency, with most leaders affirming their support for the Deputy President. MPs from the political divide who attended the ceremony  alleged there was  scheme to frustrate the DP’s 2022 presidential ambition through the ICC and constitution amendment. The DP however give the debate a wide berth instead focusing on the gender rule debate.  